ukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=cece2efb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=1240643e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=c1d6ae16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n或公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F29%2FP2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=6485ba87\" target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交表</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=3c4a2281\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=b19283a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]"},{"pid":"fa6874f4000234a6dfa7970f556f8208b735c60c","tid":1262190,"uid":103759,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a1667310f9e03d202126d11278d389f4a35dd499","tid":1262190,"uid":128989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:50:34.000Z","msg":"同老婆結婚前有共識唔生仔<br />\n講好咗養寵物 去下旅行 keep住二人世界<br />\n自從佢好姐妹生仔之後 <br />\n無啦啦母愛氾濫咁 話要生仔<br />\n成日睇bb相啊片啊 講埋咩育兒心得<br />\n最近因為呢樣嘢成日鬧交 <br />\n可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 近4字"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:06:37.000Z","msg":"咪住先 咩事咁突然 試下拖佢三個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6aba8e8ab0c70a1ead3bcd8c09e84b40a85223","tid":1262190,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"老婆幾多歲？"},{"pid":"59533330e02667206bdbfd2f64b315ac6893993e","tid":1262190,"uid":128989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ee4186761f0bad4a88b22123967fba8e06b19ab1","tid":1262190,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:02:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:09:54.000Z","msg":"暫時都得 <br />\n不過擔心日後失業點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e02d8c3aaf97694b5834ea9b69f190ea9e58bd","tid":1262190,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:11:47.000Z","msg":"咁係佢反口吖, 定其實一路都想生, 而家先現形?<br />\n有啲女人到咁上下驚個男人走佬就會想生"},{"pid":"3a63a08cb04e4f8abb17c094b1f476dbed9cd330","tid":1262190,"uid":182637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"女人好撚古惑<br />\n你老婆見到佢d姊妹生 實會覺得我都應該生番個<br />\n同埋佢d姊妹應該都有慫恿佢生<br />\n重點係你老婆幾多歲"},{"pid":"13de5b6a4ca856c378f704c0933df52bbd66b0a0","tid":1262190,"uid":151684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:14:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84f9e47fb23bef59b9739eb079bfb48776cb63d3","tid":1262190,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:15:45.000Z","msg":"可以，不過同佢講搵條後生啲嘅女幫手生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e604df715831f4ef9ea0907524d4f759091b6c6","tid":1262190,"uid":132729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:16:22.000Z","msg":"搵個巴打代你中出囉"},{"pid":"7cc587256c4462aaac4c2ecc607aa57e2159a9b9","tid":1262190,"uid":270511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:17:30.000Z","msg":"Plan 計劃"},{"pid":"8fde25644b476307ae6d3c03fa5bbff63d3770ff","tid":1262190,"uid":128989,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"799eb5823a7a12cacbdd528568ec1508a1eb9f96","tid":1262190,"uid":178682,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:04:32.000Z","msg":"想詳細知多啲點解想要細路<br />\n淨係一句母愛氾濫好難溝通"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:23:29.000Z","msg":"佢覺得好得意<br />\n又見到好姐妹成日喺fb曬相 一家三口好溫馨<br />\n同埋話我哋第日其中一個去咗 都有親人陪 (佢講呢個point果下 我有一秒動搖過 不過諗諗下如果生咗件頂心杉 就唔係咁講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"028a4a1cb229b365ec74d198bf724177926b5287","tid":1262190,"uid":128989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a6aba8e8ab0c70a1ead3bcd8c09e84b40a85223","tid":1262190,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"老婆幾多歲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:25:00.000Z","msg":"3字"},{"pid":"1235bbf28c989c8eaa65c61eb39b22161d36203a","tid":1262190,"uid":128989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5e02d8c3aaf97694b5834ea9b69f190ea9e58bd","tid":1262190,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:11:47.000Z","msg":"咁係佢反口吖, 定其實一路都想生, 而家先現形?<br />\n有啲女人到咁上下驚個男人走佬就會想生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:30:14.000Z","msg":"應該係前者 之前兩三年都沒見佢咁恨"},{"pid":"f57719f2c606750b75f089810918b634f26c16b1","tid":1262190,"uid":235764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:34:50.000Z","msg":"生女囉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問返自己，點解唔想。<br />\n如果理由係充夠就好好去溝通下。<br />\n<br />\n生小朋友唔係買玩具，<br />\n有勁大責任。<br />\n而你地要考慮唔只金錢，<br />\n其他以外嘅因素都要考慮。<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔愛你嘅小朋友就咪生。<br />\n如果愛佢就諗多d，<br />\n點教，比咩生活環境佢。<br />\n如果未來你地2腳一申，<br />\n佢一個人點算？<br />\n（所以以前d人先生一打，不過明顯不合時宜）<br />\n<br />\n好多野要諗。<br />\n<br />\n如果只係為左所謂咩女人完整性，<br />\n人類繁衍責任，甚至地族束縛，<br />\n理由實在太薄弱。<br />\n<br />\n地球眼中，我地都只係寄生蟲。"},{"pid":"a4269993f1a5492d3e1c28fb7fb3afa5800f7527","tid":1262190,"uid":252091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:39:57.000Z","msg":"先做絕育，然後晚晚中出"},{"pid":"74aa47339bbfbe46427e43add4f74259408701ce","tid":1262190,"uid":263312,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:44:49.000Z","msg":"諗清楚呀<br />\n生左小朋友你個世界可以有巨變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}